                    <div class="entry-body">		
                        <br><br> <h3 class="title"><a href="">Introduction</a></h3><br>
                        <p align ="justify">
                            Possessing a strong professional network is crucial for the survival in the corporate sector. Connecting to a professional network requires a strong personal branding for personal development and individuality. Thus, nothing can be more supportive for the fresh graduates stepping into the industry than guidance from the outstanding people in the arena. 
                        </p> <p align ="justify">
                            YOUTM will feature such personnel from the industry. The focus of the event will be on building a professional network and the concept of personal branding. The concept of personal branding creates a sense of individuality and uniqueness for a graduate entering the corporate sector, among many hundreds of graduates with various qualifications in equally demanding fields.
                        </p> <p align ="justify">
                            This will help the employers to easily distinguish a graduate from the rest. The topics covered will help the participants to understand their true potential, and hence develop an idea about their own ‘personal brand’. This will eventually enable them to establish their mark in the corporate world with value addition.
                        </p>


                        <br> <h3 class="title"><a href="">Content</a></h3><br>

                        <ul>

                            <li>• Workshop on how to develop a professional network. </li>
                            <li>• Identifying the true potential in yourself.</li>
                            <li>• Building up and Maintaining your brand within the network. </li>
                        </ul>

                        <br><br/>
                        <br> <h4>Date</h4>19th of December 2013<br>
                        <br> <h4>Time</h4>8:45 AM<br>
                        <br> <h4>Place</h4>Civil Auditorium<br>
                        <br> <h4>Speakers</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Dhananjaya Rajapaksha</strong><br>Chief Executive Officer, Brandix Casual Wear</li>
                            <li><strong>Thiagarajah Selvamoorthy</strong><br>Production Scheduler, Ceylon Tobacco Company Ltd</li>
                            <li><strong>Ahmad Aslam</strong><br>Finance Manager TaO, Ceylon Tobacco Company Ltd</li>
                        </ul>   
                        

                        <br>




